### readImpl() {#a4eafbdaec23df0b928d64cf6d16c2831}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>std::error&#95;code SampleProfileReaderGCC::readImpl ()</>}
  labels = {["virtual"]}>
Read sample profiles from the associated file.

Read a GCC AutoFDO profile.

This format is generated by the Linux Perf conversion tool at <a href="https://github.com/google/autofdo">https://github.com/google/autofdo</a>.
